parameters:
Flames flicker from the gaping hole... It seems to be an
artificial bonfire using underground gas.

...Perhaps there is simply no way to extinguish the flames. Laura
and the others' HP and MP have been fully restored.
人さらいは端っこでのびてる。
レベッカは意識を取り戻してる。

\SE[8]...Thank you, Ryan. \SE[6]I never expected you to come and
help me...

\SE[36]N-No, I mean... \SE[38]I was completely relying on Laura
and the others... \SE[37]I didn't do anything significant... Not
at all...

\SM[tremble]\SE[22]That's not true! \SE[21]Ryan, you were a great
help, right?

\SE[1]That's right. If there hadn't been any help, I wouldn't
know what would have happened.

\SE[3]...I was so happy. \SE[20] You really looked like a true
hero...
レベッカ、ライアンの目の前に接近

\SM[double]\SE[30] (When you come back... I'll give you lots and
lots... of rewards ♡. Okay... ♡?)
ラウラたちに視線移動

\SE[42]Oh... my, oh my... \SE[3]Even at that age, they're already
calling themselves couples.... \SE[8]Kids these days are so
advanced....

\SE[2]... Is that so? \SE[0] Even Laura proposed to me when we
were around that age, you know.

\SE[105]Huh...!? Uh... well... that... \SE[50]Certainly, that was
more of an impulsive act... \SM[tremble]\SE[70]You could say it
was just youthful indiscretion...
\SE[38]Was it all just a game to you...?

\SE[115]...Hawaa!! N-No, that's not it! \SM[rock]\SE[94]I mean,
it's not like I was serious or anything!! Um...!

\SE\SE[15]Oh my... I'm happy to hear that. \SE[15]Don't worry, I
understand. \SM[nod]\SE[31]I just wanted to see Laura being all
flustered...

\SE[6]I'm sorry? \SE[15]...But Laura, your movements earlier were
really good, you know? \SE[31]Rebecca-chan didn't get hurt
either, and Ryan-kun...

\SE[51]Luna is the amazing one.... \SE[52]I-I'm just... small and
insignificant...!

\SE\SM[nod]\SE[30]Don't belittle yourself, okay?
\SM[nod]\SE[30]It's alright. You're getting stronger little by
little.

\SE[30]I, who have been watching you all this time, am saying it.
\SM[nod]\SE[1]Don't worry. There's no mistake.

\SE[45]And besides... I'm praising you, so \SE[46]you should just
be happy about it... \SE[58]Understood?
ルナロア。ラウラのそばに

\SE[31] (When you come back, I'll give you lots and lots...
\SM[nod]\SE[46] of rewards... ♡ Will you let me...?)
ルナロアドットで、ふきだしかなにかで…笑える？

\SE[95]Uu... My pure maiden's heart... \SM[tremble]\SE[33]It's
being toyed with...

\SE[2]Alright, shall we go soon? \SE[0]We need to return those
kids safely too.
ルナロア下へ。画面から消える・
\SE[85]W-When will I be able to receive my r-reward...!?
ラウラ追うようにダッシュ。で終わり。
編成にレベッカも追加。
強くはないけど、ライアンよりは一回り強い
Hello. Are you a human? Do you have any business?
I will warp you to the entrance of the mine.

There's a Unique Boss on the lower floor... Hmm... I wonder what
should we do about this...

It might be a bit of a spoiler, but... Do you still want to hear
it?
I still want to hear it

Oh... Am I going to tell you that...? Well, I guess I have no
choice...

If the Unique Boss is too strong, maybe it would be better to
defeat the Story Boss first. I don't want you to ask why though.
Right. Let's pretend you didn't hear anything.
